longBusinessSummary: PVP Ventures Limited, together with its subsidiaries, develops urban infrastructure in India. The company operates through Real Estate, Media Related Activities, and Other Segments. It is also involved in the movie production and financing related activities. PVP Ventures Limited was incorporated in 1991 and is based in Hyderabad, India. PVP Ventures Limited is a subsidiary of Platex Limited.
